  "texts": [
    "VII, the performance of PCA+ is remarkably similar for both v = 1 and v = 1 × 10 -8 across most metrics.",
    "However, the FID scores for v = 1 are consistently slightly lower across all prompts and models.",
    "The marginally superior FID performance of v = 1 can be attributed to its alignment with the standard normal distribution, which is commonly used as the prior in many diffusion models.",
    "Based on this observation, we choose v = 1 for our main experiments with PCA+.TABLE VII HYPERPARAMETERS ANALYSIS ON v FOR PCA+.",
